{"tid":1719150,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［POLY］唔撚該 認清楚行動目的得唔得","createTime":"2019-11-14T04:33:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T07:00:00.000Z","uid":177115,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"5a54e9deda74b884ed568247eac745e30cd6ba03","tid":1719150,"uid":177115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T04:33:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">理工地理位置<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">好撚重要</span></span></strong>！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">守二橋係為左block 吐露港公路，</span></span></span></strong><br />\n而Poly 既地理位置<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">喺紅隧主要據點</span></span>，<br />\n而Poly 地形好閪，因為太多出入口，容易俾狗包圍同捉。<br />\n所以最好既方法係，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">同我塞滿曬個campus 摞到天橋先塞到紅隧。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家認清楚行動目的，雖然守護學校係重要，但<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>守護香港更為重要</strong></span>，阻塞主要交通幹線係令到三罷最可行，香港人<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">，唔該迅速飛入POLY支援</span></span></strong>，咪撚再嘉年華，仲有屌晒所有散水撚話棄理工。</span>"},{"pid":"b06cece4ea43d1834469d3ce7df12cc0c1722680","tid":1719150,"uid":64946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T04:34:09.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"bbb034156afee98006db0c60b742277cd6708912","tid":1719150,"uid":177115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a54e9deda74b884ed568247eac745e30cd6ba03","tid":1719150,"uid":177115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T04:33:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">理工地理位置<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">好撚重要</span></span></strong>！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">守二橋係為左block 吐露港公路，</span></span></span></strong><br />\n而Poly 既地理位置<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">喺